tags.name: Hamilton West
tags.wheelchair:description: The station sits down around 5 metres from the street so there's a long ramp that leads down to both platforms. On the Glasgow bound side be aware that this is shared with the car park so keep an eye out for traffic. The ticket office is fully accessible
